metadata.name: Enlightened
metadata.description: She is an enlightened woman with unbridled passion, spiritual powers and deep providence. She has a gift, to see the future, to inform us of a sense of freedom, to share with us the skill in everything that is subject to them. Endowed with an irresistible gaze, she is able to hypnotize even the greatest yogis, sorcerers and change her appearance at her own will. She is independent, frank and decisive, possessing the grace of spirit. Without it, the world will not reach its goal and humanity, like the entire planet, will remain barren.
